# Documentation standards

## Language

- User-facing docs: **English**
- UI strings in code: Russian (unless i18n task)

## Maintainer

Always credit **FLOWAXY DIGITAL STUDIO** as current maintainer.  
Original authors: HOSTINPL (HOSTING-RUS), 2020.

## Required links in install/deploy docs

- CDN: `https://code.flowaxy.com/hostpanel`
- Repo: `https://github.com/iteffa-works/hostinpl.pl`
- Donate: `https://flowaxy.com/donate`

## When editing docs

- Update `CHANGELOG.md` Unreleased for notable changes
- Cross-link `.docs/README.md` index
- Mention large binaries are CDN-only (not in Git)
- Use `config.example.php` not `config.php` in examples
